net.wequick.small

Class WebBundleLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.wequick.small.BundleLauncher
      • net.wequick.small.SoBundleLauncher
        • net.wequick.small.AssetBundleLauncher
          • net.wequick.small.WebBundleLauncher

  • public class WebBundleLauncher
extends AssetBundleLauncher
    This class launch the plugin html file with an internal WebActivity.

    It resolves the bundle who's pkg is specified as "*.web.*" in bundle.json.

    The WebActivity takes the WebView as content view to show html content.

    For speeding up the loading of html content, we use the WebViewPool to manager the web views.

    See Also:
    WebActivity, WebView, WebViewPool
